{"tid":1024183,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[外匯] 好Zone分享: CAD/JPY","createTime":"2019-02-16T10:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T06:07:21.000Z","uid":43407,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c643c383839a20d129d13e662c7f992977b0aa5e","tid":1024183,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A5%BDzone%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-cadjpy/2291558747792723/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F%25E5%25A1%25B5%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E7%259E%25AC%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258C%25AFk%25E6%2588%25BF%2F%25E5%25A5%25BDzone%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25BA%25AB-cadjpy%2F2291558747792723%2F&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=b9e48512\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A5%BDzone%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-cadjpy/2291558747792723/</a><br />\n<br />\n豬年第一po，先祝各位萬事勝意，一本萬利！今天簡單和大家分享一個靚zone，加圓兌日圓的Sell order flow zone。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkrbnNB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkrbnNB.png&h=3cb4d9ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日圖顯示過去一年Cad/Jpy是下行趨勢，價格在上月初閃崩後繼續回升，差不多到達Sell zone的位置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpu00zp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmpu00zp.png&h=9c5dd82b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四小時圖上，價格在85.23之上徘徊一段時間後，稍稍上升至86.22便無法繼續，並頗急速地下跌，之後曾試圖上試但亦無法突破85.23，隨後便一直向下。顯示在這個區間內的買賣失衡，急速下跌代表有很多大戶賣單無法被成交。因此，若之後價格重回85.23 - 86.22 這個Sell zone，值得我們加倍留意。"},{"pid":"792d303e50fa9e52d38e03dce7d94e51ac8c613b","tid":1024183,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb3b8c601dec989fa5d6aa901ff1b6cee061bcb","tid":1024183